  <front>
   <head>For my own Tomb-stone.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="triplet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Me 'twas giv'n to die: to Thee 'tis giv'n</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">To live: Alas! one Moment sets us ev'n.</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Mark! how impartial is the Will of Heav'n?</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
